query:
SELECT 
  TABLE_NAME,
  COLUMN_NAME
FROM 
  INFORMATION_SCHEMA.COLUMNS
WHERE 
  TABLE_SCHEMA = DATABASE()
  AND COLUMN_NAME LIKE '%message%'
ORDER BY 
  TABLE_NAME, COLUMN_NAME;
